»KENNETH NELSON
1930         (ACTOR)          1993    
(TEXAS)                          (LONDON)
       Life was FANTASTIC      
                                      NAOMI"║
ÀAlisa 28.05.1963 - 20.03.2016
You are my listener, my support, my ambition.
You are my imagination, my right hand, my precision.
Simply put in one word - you are my beloved Mother."╝
╣Sweet Thames, run softly, till I find my song

For Jon who loved this river,
From Madeleine who loved Jon
And from Joshua his son

The Hon Jonathan James Lewin 20.5.1959-10.5.2000"┐
