¢SARAH LAKE
25th October 1979 - 30th August 2013
Beloved wife, daughter, sister and friend
Forever loved, always missed, never forgotten
We all miss you so much
Jamie, Thomas and Spanky"╩
ÃTo Our Beloved Robert Burness
02.07.1950 - 16.05.2010
That laughing eye, whose sunny beam
Our memory would not cherish less,
And oh, that smile! whose joyous gleam
No mortal language can express"╠
